name: Route 66 - Tandem
additionalNotes:
Parts of AKA Cigars, first introduced at the 2105 ICPCR show. this cigar is a unique idea as it is capped at both ends and has a line of tobacco in the center marking off a section to cut if one wishes to share the massive cigar with a friend
Details
Wrapper is Ecuador-grown Cuban seed Habano 
Binder is  Jalapa Criollo
